####Elbow methods
### Use map_dbl to run many models with varying value of k (centers)
tot_withinss <- purrr::map_dbl(1:10, function(k){
  model<-kmeans(x=dataFrame, centers = k, nstart = 25)
  model$tot.withinss
})
